# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Rendered output — never commit pixels (PNG/mp4) or raw pixel-buffer dumps
**/out/
**/*.png
**/*.mp4
**/*.mov
**/*.webm
**/*.raw
**/_diag-crops/
**/critic-crops/
**/_pick-crops/
.tmp_crops/

# Remotion / bundler scratch
.remotion/

# Strip manifests are tiny JSON but live beside output dirs; keep them out too
**/strip-manifest.json

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
